features: 【Upgrade Design】The plant shelf indoor includes 10 shelves that hold 11 regular-sized pots and after upgraded the plant shelves can hang pots or place tall plants on the middle level of the shelf. Save space while allowing each layer of plants to get plenty of sunlight. Tip: It is recommended to place heavy plants on the bottom and light plants on top. The plant holders indoor stand can hold up to 150 lbs.

【Large Capacity & Multiple Usage】The unique design of our outdoor plant stand can not only place flower pots, but also storage boxes, ornaments, books, shoes, photo albums and other supplies. And the tall plant stand can be placed in different places such as bedroom, living room, corner, balcony, courtyard, etc., to help you save more indoor or outdoor space. Also, the flower stand is an ideal gift for gardening enthusiasts, friends and neighbors.

【100% Solid Wood, Sturdy & Durable】The plant racks are made of high-quality wood and carbonized at high temperatures. More durable and easy to clean. No paint surface, healthy and eco-friendly, so the indoor plant stand is very safe for families with children and pregnant women. And the corner plant stand can be used indoors and outdoors.

【Easy To Assemble】Upgraded ASB plastic triangle connectors make the outdoor plant shelf more sturdy and easier to install. We have prepared instructions, hammers and gloves in the package to make it easier for you to assemble the plant stand. Wear gloves before installation to avoid hurting or getting your hands dirty.

【Customer Service】If you find that there is a problem with the product after you receive it, or you don't know how to install the corner plant shelf, please feel free to contact us, we will provide you with services in time until the problem is solved!

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Uneedem 10 Tiered Plant Stand Are your plants still scattered around corners? Are you still struggling with not knowing how to organize them? Act now! Organizing plants on a large plant stand will save you a lot of space and can decorate your room.

Made of solid wood, our plant stands for indoor plants are sturdy and durable and can hold up to 150 pounds. No paint on the surface, so it is very safe for families with children and pregnant women. Our plant pot stands are carbonized at high temperature for longer life, not easy to get wet, and easy to clean. The ASB plastic connector adopts a triangular structure to make the wood plant stand more stable. And the triangular connection port is easier to install. 11-inch wooden tray that can hold multiple pots. And after an upgraded design, the middle layer of our plant table can place tall plants.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 14, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars My Plants Love It
reviews.reviewText: I need a cheap plant shelf to make the best use of my picture window. Found these low cost shelves online and couldn't be happier.They are cheap and smaller than you'd expect (you may note I used crates to elevate them a bit in front of my window (it worked perfectly).The shelving is good enough quality to hold plants of different sizes and weights. It feels steady and should last the test of time.Assembly was straightforward once you get the hang of it. The mallet included was perfect and worked VERY WELL despite others saying it broke. I saved it to use on other projects. It looked me 23 mins to assemble the stand shelf from start to finish.I ended up ordering 3 more of them (they look great and made more space to buy more plants lol). I couldn't be more pleased.The gloves included are handy and kept my hands cleaned during assembly (as your hands will get dirty but it washes off easily). The tiny garden tools are cute but prob won't serve much of a purpose for me.I would recommend the stands but would recommend checking out the dimensions as it is smaller than it appears online.Overall I'm very pleased and would recommend and would big again. (I could almost use one of these for every window at my house 🙈).

When redoing my plant room, I needed shelves that could hold numerous plants with differing heights, not have solid shelving, so as to let in light, fit into my space, and not be too expensive. I spent a long time checking measurements and configurations. I ended up getting four units from different companies, but they are all the same material, construction, and assembly. I guess they are made by the same company, but are from different distributors. Anyway, I am a super pleased with them all. They were easy to put together, have a nice look, are pretty sturdy, even with heavy pots, and are a good price. They are 12" deep; which allows more floor space in a smaller room. I will post this review on all the sellers sites that I have bought these from, so they all have the same review.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 26, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Better than nothing
reviews.reviewText: I needed to get some plants off the floor but didn't want to spend the money on another metal shelf. I knew for $25 it wasn't going to be great quality. It took about 25 minutes to out together. A lot of the pieces were warped, twisted, or cut just a little too long so it took a lot of banging to get them connected. Most of the shelves were also warped. It does not sit flat on the floor so will probably need to wedge something under some of the legs. Even knowing the measurements when I ordered it, it is smaller than you would expect. Wear the gloves because your hands will get the carbon on them. Plus the gloves help with all of the splinters that came off of the pieces. You get what you pay for. It is ok for a quick setup when money is tight but not sure I would buy another one.
